This report shows profit and loss of each stock you traded.

It includes Stocks, Options, Dividends, Stock/Option Fee, Margin Interest and Subscription Fee. 
Rest all transactions are NOT covered.

Important : This extension stores all your trading information in your local system. Avoid using it on public systems.

Note: This report can be updated only on non-trading hours or weekends. For ex: 8:00AM to 3:00PM CST cannot be updated.

* The numbers may not match with Robinhood numbers due to variety of reasons like decimal places, fees, adjustments etc.,.

Chrome Version must be greater than v80. Doesn't work on lower versions.
Not tested on MAC and any other non-desktop devices.
